<section class="sec" id="s1">
  <div class="sec-hdr"><span class="sec-num">01</span><h2 class="sec-h2">Soma dos ângulos internos do triângulo</h2></div>
  <div class="concept"><div class="c-tag">Propriedade fundamental</div><p>A soma dos três ângulos internos de <strong>qualquer triângulo</strong> é sempre <strong>180°</strong>.</p></div>
  <div class="formula"><small>Propriedade</small>∠A + ∠B + ∠C = 180°</div>
  <div class="tip info"><span>💡</span><div>No triângulo retângulo, ∠B = 90°, então os outros dois somam 90° (são complementares).</div></div>

  <div class="example" id="ex1">
    <div class="ex-head" onclick="tog('ex1')"><span class="ex-badge">Q1</span><h4>Triângulo com ângulo reto e 37°. Qual é o terceiro ângulo?</h4><span class="ex-arr">▼</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <div class="ex-inner">
        <div class="ex-steps">
          <ul class="steps">
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">1</span><span>Triângulo retângulo: <strong>∠B = 90°</strong></span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">2</span><span>90° + 37° + x = 180°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">3</span><span>127° + x = 180°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">4</span><span>x = 53°</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="ans">Resposta: x = <strong>53°</strong></div>
        </div>
        <!-- A=topo-esq(30,20), B=base-esq(30,160), C=base-dir(170,160). Ângulo reto em B. 37° em A entre AB e AC. x em C. -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 210 185" width="200" height="175" style="flex-shrink:0">
          <polygon points="30,20 30,160 170,160" fill="#EEF2FF" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/>
          <rect x="30" y="144" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <text x="18" y="16" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">A</text>
          <!-- 37° em A: arco entre dir AB (↓) e dir AC (→↓ 45°). r=22.
               start(dir AB, r=22): (30, 20+22)=(30,42)
               end(dir AC=45°, r=22): (30+22*cos45°,20+22*sin45°)=(30+15.6,20+15.6)=(45.6,35.6) -->
          <path d="M30,42 A22,22 0 0,1 46,36" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="49" y="48" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">37°</text>
          <text x="10" y="176" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">B</text>
          <text x="2" y="144" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">reto</text>
          <text x="4" y="156" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">90°</text>
          <text x="172" y="176" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">C</text>
          <!-- x em C: arco entre dir CB (←, 180°) e dir CA (↑←, 225°). r=22.
               start(dir CB, r=22): (170-22,160)=(148,160)
               end(dir CA=225°, r=22): (170+22*cos225°,160+22*sin225°)=(170-15.6,160-15.6)=(154.4,144.4) -->
          <path d="M148,160 A22,22 0 0,0 154,144" fill="#FEE2E2" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="132" y="150" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#DC2626">x</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="example" id="ex2">
    <div class="ex-head" onclick="tog('ex2')"><span class="ex-badge">Q2</span><h4>Os ângulos internos medem 2x, 3x e 4x. Qual é o valor de x?</h4><span class="ex-arr">▼</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <div class="ex-inner">
        <div class="ex-steps">
          <ul class="steps">
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">1</span><span>2x + 3x + 4x = 180°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">2</span><span>9x = 180°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">3</span><span>x = 20°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">4</span><span>Ângulos: 40°, 60° e 80°</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="ans">Resposta: x = <strong>20°</strong></div>
        </div>
        <!-- A=topo(100,18), B=base-esq(20,165), C=base-dir(180,165) -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 210 185" width="200" height="175" style="flex-shrink:0">
          <polygon points="100,18 20,165 180,165" fill="#FFF7ED" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/>
          <text x="93" y="13" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">A</text>
          <!-- 2x em A: dir AB=atan2(147,-80)≈118.6°, dir AC=atan2(147,80)≈61.4°. Arco entre 61.4° e 118.6°, r=22.
               start(61.4°): (100+22*cos61.4°,18+22*sin61.4°)=(100+10.6,18+19.3)=(110.6,37.3)
               end(118.6°):  (100+22*cos118.6°,18+22*sin118.6°)=(100-10.6,18+19.3)=(89.4,37.3) -->
          <path d="M111,37 A22,22 0 0,1 89,37" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="88" y="54" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">2x</text>
          <text x="4" y="180" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">B</text>
          <!-- 3x em B(20,165): dir BC=(160,0)→0°, dir BA=(-80,-147)→atan2(-147,80 invertido)→ acima direita em SVG
               No SVG (y pra baixo): dir BA vetor(80,-147) → atan2(-147,80)≈-61.4°=298.6°
               arco de 0° até 298.6° (sweep=0 = anti-horário no SVG, menor arco de 0° para 298.6°)
               r=26:
               start(dir BC→0°, r=26): (20+26,165)=(46,165)
               end(dir BA→-61.4°, r=26): (20+26*cos(-61.4°),165+26*sin(-61.4°))
                   =(20+26*0.479,165+26*(-0.878))=(20+12.5,165-22.8)=(32.5,142.2) -->
          <path d="M46,165 A26,26 0 0,0 33,143" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="46" y="158" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">3x</text>
          <text x="183" y="180" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">C</text>
          <!-- 4x em C(180,165): dir CB=(-160,0)→180°, dir CA=(-80,-147)→ acima esquerda em SVG
               dir CA vetor(-80,-147) em SVG: atan2(-147,-80)≈-118.6°=241.4°
               arco de 180° até 241.4°, r=26:
               start(dir CB→180°, r=26): (180-26,165)=(154,165)
               end(dir CA→-118.6°, r=26): (180+26*cos(-118.6°),165+26*sin(-118.6°))
                   =(180-26*0.479,165-26*0.878)=(180-12.5,165-22.8)=(167.5,142.2) -->
          <path d="M154,165 A26,26 0 0,1 168,143" fill="#FEE2E2" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="144" y="157" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#DC2626">4x</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- S2 -->
<section class="sec" id="s2">
  <div class="sec-hdr"><span class="sec-num">02</span><h2 class="sec-h2">Ângulos suplementares e complementares</h2></div>
  <div class="two-col">
    <div><div class="concept"><div class="c-tag">Suplementares</div><p>Dois ângulos somam <strong>180°</strong> — completam uma linha reta.</p></div><div class="formula"><small>Suplementares</small>α + β = 180°</div></div>
    <div><div class="concept"><div class="c-tag">Complementares</div><p>Dois ângulos somam <strong>90°</strong> — completam um ângulo reto.</p></div><div class="formula"><small>Complementares</small>α + β = 90°</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tip warn"><span>⚠️</span><div><strong>Não confunda!</strong> Suplementar → 180°. Complementar → 90°.</div></div>

  <div class="example" id="ex3">
    <div class="ex-head" onclick="tog('ex3')"><span class="ex-badge">Q3</span><h4>Suplementar de 128° — qual é o outro ângulo?</h4><span class="ex-arr">▼</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <div class="ex-inner">
        <div class="ex-steps">
          <ul class="steps">
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">1</span><span>Suplementares somam 180°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">2</span><span>128° + x = 180°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">3</span><span>x = 52°</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="ans">Resposta: x = <strong>52°</strong></div>
        </div>
        <!-- Linha reta, ponto central em (130,75). Raio a 52° acima da horizontal (= 128° do lado esq).
             128° do lado esq significa que o raio está a 180°-128°=52° da direita.
             Raio endpoint (comprimento 60): (130+60*cos52°,75-60*sin52°)=(130+36.9,75-47.3)=(166.9,27.7)≈(167,28)
             Arco 128° (lado esq, azul): de dir esq (r=50, ponto (80,75)) até dir raio (r=50):
               (130+50*cos52°,75-50*sin52°)=(130+30.8,75-39.4)=(160.8,35.6)≈(161,36)
             Arco x (lado dir, verde): de dir raio (r=50, ponto (161,36)) até dir dir (r=50, ponto (180,75)):
        -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 260 125" width="250" height="120" style="flex-shrink:0">
          <line x1="10" y1="75" x2="250" y2="75" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <polygon points="10,75 18,71 18,79" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
          <polygon points="250,75 242,71 242,79" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
          <circle cx="130" cy="75" r="3" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
          <line x1="130" y1="75" x2="167" y2="28" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Arco 128° (esq, azul): sweep=1 (horário no SVG = preenche o ângulo obtuso à esq) -->
          <path d="M80,75 A50,50 0 0,1 161,36" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.75"/>
          <text x="70" y="64" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">128°</text>
          <!-- Arco x (dir, verde): de (161,36) até (180,75), sweep=1 -->
          <path d="M161,36 A50,50 0 0,1 180,75" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="172" y="52" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">x</text>
          <line x1="10" y1="90" x2="10" y2="97" stroke="#777" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="10" y1="97" x2="250" y2="97" stroke="#777" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="250" y1="90" x2="250" y2="97" stroke="#777" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="130" y1="97" x2="130" y2="104" stroke="#777" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="130" y="118" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="800" fill="#1a1e3a">180°</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="example" id="ex6">
    <div class="ex-head" onclick="tog('ex6')"><span class="ex-badge b2">Q6</span><h4>Complementar de 34° — qual é o outro ângulo?</h4><span class="ex-arr">▼</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <div class="ex-inner">
        <div class="ex-steps">
          <ul class="steps">
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">1</span><span>Complementares somam 90°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">2</span><span>34° + x = 90°</span></li>
            <li class="step"><span class="sc">3</span><span>x = 56°</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="ans">Resposta: x = <strong>56°</strong></div>
        </div>
        <!-- Origem O=(50,155). Eixo vertical para cima, horizontal para direita.
             Raio oblíquo: 34° da vertical = 56° da horizontal.
             cos56°≈0.559, sin56°≈0.829. Len=100.
             Endpoint: (50+100*0.559, 155-100*0.829)=(105.9,72.1)≈(106,72)
             
             Ângulo 34° (azul): entre eixo vertical e raio.
               dir vertical (cima, SVG): ângulo=-90° (ou 270°)
               dir raio: ângulo=-56° (acima da horizontal)
               r=38: 
               start(dir vertical, r=38): (50,155-38)=(50,117)
               end(dir raio a -56°, r=38): (50+38*cos(-56°),155+38*sin(-56°))
                   =(50+38*0.559,155-38*0.829)=(50+21.2,155-31.5)=(71.2,123.5)≈(71,124)
               sweep=1 (horário no SVG, de cima para o raio) ✓
               
             Ângulo x=56° (verde): entre raio e eixo horizontal.
               dir raio: -56°, dir horizontal: 0°
               r=38:
               start(dir raio, r=38): (71,124) como acima
               end(dir horizontal, r=38): (50+38,155)=(88,155)
               sweep=1 (horário no SVG, do raio para horizontal) ✓
        -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 210 185" width="200" height="175" style="flex-shrink:0">
          <line x1="50" y1="155" x2="190" y2="155" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <polygon points="190,155 182,151 182,159" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="155" x2="50" y2="18" stroke="#2563EB" stroke-width="2"/>
          <polygon points="50,18 46,26 54,26" fill="#2563EB"/>
          <rect x="50" y="139" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="155" x2="106" y2="72" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Arco 34° (azul, entre vertical e raio) -->
          <path d="M50,117 A38,38 0 0,1 71,124" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="2" y="118" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">Ângulo 1</text>
          <text x="4" y="130" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="800" fill="#2563EB">34°</text>
          <!-- Arco x=56° (verde, entre raio e horizontal) -->
          <path d="M71,124 A38,38 0 0,1 88,155" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="90" y="143" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">Ângulo 2</text>
          <text x="96" y="157" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="800" fill="#059669">x°</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- S3 -->
<section class="sec" id="s3">
  <div class="sec-hdr"><span class="sec-num">03</span><h2 class="sec-h2">Retas paralelas e transversal</h2></div>
  <div class="two-col">
    <div>
      <div class="concept"><div class="c-tag">Conceito</div><p>Quando uma reta <strong>transversal</strong> corta duas retas <strong>paralelas</strong>, formam-se 8 ângulos com relações especiais.</p></div>
      <div class="formula"><small>Correspondentes</small>Mesmo lado → iguais</div>
      <div class="formula"><small>Alternos internos</small>Lados opostos → iguais</div>
      <div class="formula"><small>Co-internos</small>Mesmo lado → soma = 180°</div>
    </div>
    <!-- Transversal: de (165,5) a (90,195). Cruza r(y=65) em x=141, cruza s(y=145) em x=110.
         Dir transversal (descendo): vetor(-75,190), ângulo=atan2(190,-75)≈111.5°
         115° é o ângulo OBTUSO entre a direita de r (0°) e a transversal descendo (111.5°): 111.5° ≈ 115° ✓
         Arco 115° em P_r(141,65): de dir direita (r=30, ponto (171,65)) até dir transversal descendo (r=30):
           end: (141+30*cos111.5°,65+30*sin111.5°)=(141-11,65+27.9)=(130,92.9)≈(130,93)
           sweep=1 (preenche o ângulo entre a direita e a transversal descendo, sentido horário no SVG)
         Arco correspondente x em P_s(110,145): mesma geometria.
           start dir direita (r=30): (110+30,145)=(140,145)
           end dir transversal descendo (r=30): (110+30*cos111.5°,145+30*sin111.5°)=(110-11,145+28)=(99,173)
    -->
    <div class="vis-box">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 240 200" width="230" height="190">
        <line x1="10" y1="65" x2="225" y2="65" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="2"/>
        <polygon points="10,65 18,61 18,69" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
        <polygon points="225,65 217,61 217,69" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
        <text x="6" y="57" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="800" font-style="italic" fill="#1a1e3a">r</text>
        <line x1="10" y1="145" x2="225" y2="145" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="2"/>
        <polygon points="10,145 18,141 18,149" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
        <polygon points="225,145 217,141 217,149" fill="#1a1e3a"/>
        <text x="6" y="137" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="800" font-style="italic" fill="#1a1e3a">s</text>
        <line x1="165" y1="5" x2="90" y2="195" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="167" y="13" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="800" font-style="italic" fill="#1a1e3a">t</text>
        <!-- 115° em r: de dir direita até transversal descendo (obtuso) -->
        <path d="M171,65 A30,30 0 1,0 130,93" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
        <text x="153" y="53" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">115°</text>
        <!-- x em s: arco correspondente (mesma posição) -->
        <path d="M140,145 A30,30 0 1,0 99,173" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
        <text x="122" y="178" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">x</text>
        <line x1="141" y1="65" x2="110" y2="145" stroke="#aaa" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
  <table class="ptable">
    <thead><tr><th>Par de ângulos</th><th>Posição</th><th>Relação</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Correspondentes</td><td>Mesmo lado, posição igual</td><td class="res">Iguais</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Alternos internos</td><td>Lados opostos, entre as paralelas</td><td class="res">Iguais</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Alternos externos</td><td>Lados opostos, fora das paralelas</td><td class="res">Iguais</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Co-internos</td><td>Mesmo lado, entre as paralelas</td><td class="res">Soma = 180°</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="example" id="ex4">
    <div class="ex-head" onclick="tog('ex4')"><span class="ex-badge">Q4</span><h4>Transversal forma 115° com r. Qual é o ângulo correspondente x em s?</h4><span class="ex-arr">▼</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <ul class="steps">
        <li class="step"><span class="sc">1</span><span>Ângulos correspondentes ficam na <strong>mesma posição</strong> nas duas paralelas.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span class="sc">2</span><span>Entre retas paralelas, correspondentes são <strong>iguais</strong>.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span class="sc">3</span><span>x = 115°</span></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="ans">Resposta: x = <strong>115°</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- S4 -->
<section class="sec" id="s4">
  <div class="sec-hdr"><span class="sec-num">04</span><h2 class="sec-h2">Soma dos ângulos internos de polígonos</h2></div>
  <div class="two-col">
    <div>
      <div class="concept"><div class="c-tag">Fórmula geral</div><p>Qualquer polígono convexo com <em>n</em> lados pode ser dividido em <strong>(n − 2) triângulos</strong>. Cada triângulo soma 180°.</p></div>
      <div class="formula"><small>Fórmula — polígono convexo</small>S = (n − 2) × 180°</div>
    </div>
    <div class="vis-box">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 230 195" width="220" height="185">
        <polygon points="115,15 200,58 200,138 115,182 30,138 30,58" fill="rgba(59,91,219,.08)" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/>
        <line x1="115" y1="15" x2="200" y2="138" stroke="#e8900a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5"/>
        <line x1="115" y1="15" x2="115" y2="182" stroke="#e8900a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5"/>
        <line x1="115" y1="15" x2="30" y2="138" stroke="#e8900a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5"/>
        <text x="150" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#e8900a" font-weight="700">▲1</text>
        <text x="158" y="134" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#e8900a" font-weight="700">▲2</text>
        <text x="115" y="158" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#e8900a" font-weight="700">▲3</text>
        <text x="72" y="134" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#e8900a" font-weight="700">▲4</text>
        <text x="80" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#e8900a" font-weight="700">▲5</text>
        <text x="115" y="193" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono,monospace" font-size="10" fill="#5a6490">hexágono → 4 triângulos → 720°</text>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin:1.5rem 0">
    <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem">Galeria — clique para carregar na calculadora</div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center" id="poly-gallery"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="calc">
    <div class="calc-title">⬡ Calculadora de polígonos</div>
    <div class="calc-row"><span class="calc-lbl">Número de lados (n):</span><input class="calc-in" type="number" id="cn" min="3" max="20" value="5" oninput="calcPoly()"></div>
    <div class="calc-fml" id="cfml">S = (5 − 2) × 180°</div>
    <div class="calc-out" id="cout">= 540°</div>
    <div class="calc-visual"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 180" width="200" height="180" id="calc-poly-svg"></svg></div>
  </div>
  <div class="example" id="ex5e">
    <div class="ex-head" onclick="tog('ex5e')"><span class="ex-badge bg">EXTRA</span><h4>Polígono com soma = 1260°. Quantos lados possui?</h4><span class="ex-arr">▼</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <ul class="steps">
        <li class="step"><span class="sc">1</span><span>(n − 2) × 180° = 1260°</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span class="sc">2</span><span>n − 2 = 1260 ÷ 180 = 7</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span class="sc">3</span><span>n = 9</span></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="ans">Resposta: <strong>9 lados</strong> — nonágono</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <table class="ptable">
    <thead><tr><th>Polígono</th><th>Lados (n)</th><th>Triângulos</th><th>Cálculo</th><th>Soma</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Triângulo</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>(3−2)×180°</td><td class="res">180°</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Quadrilátero</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>(4−2)×180°</td><td class="res">360°</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Pentágono ★</strong></td><td>5</td><td>3</td><td>(5−2)×180°</td><td class="res">540°</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Heptágono ★</strong></td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>(7−2)×180°</td><td class="res">900°</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Octógono ★</strong></td><td>8</td><td>6</td><td>(8−2)×180°</td><td class="res">1080°</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Decágono ★</strong></td><td>10</td><td>8</td><td>(10−2)×180°</td><td class="res">1440°</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- S5 -->
<section class="sec" id="s5">
  <div class="sec-hdr"><span class="sec-num">05</span><h2 class="sec-h2">Verdadeiro ou falso — clique para revelar</h2></div>
  <div class="tip warn"><span>👆</span><div>Tente responder mentalmente antes de clicar!</div></div>
  <div class="tf-grid">
    <div class="tf-item" data-a="V" onclick="revTF(this)"><span class="tf-num">a)</span><div><div>A soma dos ângulos internos de qualquer triângulo é 180°.</div><div class="tf-exp">Sempre verdadeira — propriedade fundamental.</div></div><span class="tf-badge">✓ VERDADEIRO</span></div>
    <div class="tf-item" data-a="F" onclick="revTF(this)"><span class="tf-num">b)</span><div><div>Um triângulo pode ter dois ângulos retos.</div><div class="tf-exp">Impossível: 90°+90°=180°, não sobra ângulo para o terceiro vértice.</div></div><span class="tf-badge">✗ FALSO</span></div>
    <div class="tf-item" data-a="V" onclick="revTF(this)"><span class="tf-num">c)</span><div><div>A soma dos ângulos internos de um quadrilátero é 360°.</div><div class="tf-exp">S=(4−2)×180°=360°. Correto!</div></div><span class="tf-badge">✓ VERDADEIRO</span></div>
    <div class="tf-item" data-a="F" onclick="revTF(this)"><span class="tf-num">d)</span><div><div>A soma dos ângulos internos de um pentágono é 520°.</div><div class="tf-exp">Errado! S=(5−2)×180°=540°, não 520°.</div></div><span class="tf-badge">✗ FALSO</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- QUIZ -->
<section class="sec" id="quiz">
  <div class="quiz-hdr"><span class="sec-num" style="display:inline-block;margin-bottom:.5rem">QUIZ</span><h2 class="sec-h2" style="font-size:2rem">Teste seus conhecimentos</h2></div>
  <div class="score-row">
    <div class="sc-card"><div class="sc-num" id="sq-c">0</div><div class="sc-lbl">Acertos</div></div>
    <div class="sc-card"><div class="sc-num" id="sq-d">0</div><div class="sc-lbl">Respondidas</div></div>
    <div class="sc-card"><div class="sc-num" id="sq-p">—</div><div class="sc-lbl">Aproveitamento</div></div>
  </div>
  <div id="qc"></div>
</section>
</main>
<footer>Geometria · 9.º Ano · Colégio Adventista · Ângulos e Polígonos</footer>

<script>
window.addEventListener('scroll',()=>{const d=document.documentElement,p=d.scrollHeight-d.clientHeight;document.getElementById('prog').style.width=(p>0?d.scrollTop/p*100:0)+'%'});
function toggleSB(){document.getElementById('sidebar').classList.toggle('open')}
document.addEventListener('click',e=>{const sb=document.getElementById('sidebar'),btn=document.getElementById('toggle');if(sb.classList.contains('open')&&!sb.contains(e.target)&&e.target!==btn)sb.classList.remove('open')});
const io=new IntersectionObserver(es=>es.forEach(e=>{if(e.isIntersecting)e.target.classList.add('vis')}),{threshold:.1});
document.querySelectorAll('.sec').forEach(s=>io.observe(s));
const nls=document.querySelectorAll('.sb-nav a');
const io2=new IntersectionObserver(es=>es.forEach(e=>{if(e.isIntersecting){const id=e.target.id;nls.forEach(a=>a.classList.toggle('act',a.getAttribute('href')==='#'+id))}}),{threshold:.3});
document.querySelectorAll('.sec').forEach(s=>io2.observe(s));
function tog(id){document.getElementById(id).classList.toggle('open')}
function revTF(el){el.classList.add('revealed');el.onclick=null}
function polyPoints(n,cx,cy,r){return Array.from({length:n},(_,i)=>{const a=(i*2*Math.PI/n)-Math.PI/2;return`${(cx+r*Math.cos(a)).toFixed(1)},${(cy+r*Math.sin(a)).toFixed(1)}`}).join(' ')}
const polys=[{n:3,sum:180,c:'#d63939'},{n:4,sum:360,c:'#e8900a'},{n:5,sum:540,c:'#3b5bdb',s:true},{n:6,sum:720,c:'#0ca678'},{n:7,sum:900,c:'#3b5bdb',s:true},{n:8,sum:1080,c:'#e8900a',s:true},{n:9,sum:1260,c:'#d63939'},{n:10,sum:1440,c:'#0ca678',s:true}];
const names=['Triângulo','Quadrilátero','Pentágono','Hexágono','Heptágono','Octógono','Nonágono','Decágono'];
const gal=document.getElementById('poly-gallery');
polys.forEach((p,i)=>{
  const div=document.createElement('div');
  div.style.cssText=`cursor:pointer;text-align:center;padding:10px 8px;border:${p.s?'2px':'1.5px'} solid ${p.s?p.c:'#dde3f5'};border-radius:10px;background:${p.s?'rgba(59,91,219,.04)':'white'};transition:all .15s;min-width:82px;box-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(59,91,219,.07)`;
  div.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 70 70" width="54" height="54"><polygon points="${polyPoints(p.n,35,35,28)}" fill="${p.c}" fill-opacity=".12" stroke="${p.c}" stroke-width="${p.s?2:1.5}"/></svg><div style="font-family:JetBrains Mono,monospace;font-size:9px;color:#5a6490;margin-top:2px">${p.n} lados${p.s?' ★':''}</div><div style="font-family:Nunito,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:${p.c}">${p.sum}°</div>`;
  div.addEventListener('mouseenter',()=>{div.style.borderColor=p.c;div.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'});
  div.addEventListener('mouseleave',()=>{div.style.borderColor=p.s?p.c:'#dde3f5';div.style.transform='none'});
  div.addEventListener('click',()=>{document.getElementById('cn').value=p.n;calcPoly()});
  gal.appendChild(div);
});
function calcPoly(){
  const n=parseInt(document.getElementById('cn').value)||3;
  const safe=Math.max(3,Math.min(20,n)),s=(safe-2)*180;
  document.getElementById('cfml').textContent=`S = (${safe} − 2) × 180°`;
  document.getElementById('cout').textContent=`= ${s}°`;
  const svg=document.getElementById('calc-poly-svg');
  svg.innerHTML=`<polygon points="${polyPoints(safe,100,88,76)}" fill="#3b5bdb" fill-opacity=".1" stroke="#3b5bdb" stroke-width="2"/><text x="100" y="93" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="15" fill="#3b5bdb" font-weight="800">${s}°</text><text x="100" y="110" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono,monospace" font-size="11" fill="#5a6490">${safe} lados</text>`;
}
calcPoly();

function mkSvgTri1(){return`<svg viewBox="0 0 180 165" width="160" height="148"><polygon points="30,18 30,148 158,148" fill="#EEF2FF" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.6"/><rect x="30" y="132" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.4"/><text x="18" y="14" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">A</text><path d="M30,38 A20,20 0 0,1 44,32" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="46" y="44" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">37°</text><text x="10" y="162" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">B</text><text x="2" y="132" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">90°</text><text x="160" y="162" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">C</text><path d="M138,148 A20,20 0 0,0 144,132" fill="#FEE2E2" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="120" y="138" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#DC2626">x</text></svg>`}
function mkSvgTri2(){return`<svg viewBox="0 0 180 165" width="160" height="148"><polygon points="90,15 18,152 162,152" fill="#FFF7ED" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.6"/><text x="83" y="11" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">A</text><path d="M100,33 A20,20 0 0,1 80,33" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="79" y="50" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">2x</text><text x="2" y="165" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">B</text><path d="M42,152 A24,24 0 0,0 30,131" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="42" y="144" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">3x</text><text x="164" y="165" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#1a1e3a">C</text><path d="M138,152 A24,24 0 0,1 150,131" fill="#FEE2E2" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="128" y="144" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#DC2626">4x</text></svg>`}
function mkSvgSup(){return`<svg viewBox="0 0 230 110" width="210" height="100"><line x1="10" y1="68" x2="220" y2="68" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/><polygon points="10,68 18,64 18,72" fill="#1a1e3a"/><polygon points="220,68 212,64 212,72" fill="#1a1e3a"/><circle cx="115" cy="68" r="3" fill="#1a1e3a"/><line x1="115" y1="68" x2="150" y2="24" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/><path d="M69,68 A46,46 0 0,1 147,33" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.75"/><text x="62" y="58" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">128°</text><path d="M147,33 A46,46 0 0,1 161,68" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="155" y="48" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">x</text></svg>`}
function mkSvgPar(){return`<svg viewBox="0 0 210 175" width="190" height="160"><line x1="8" y1="55" x2="198" y2="55" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/><polygon points="8,55 16,51 16,59" fill="#1a1e3a"/><polygon points="198,55 190,51 190,59" fill="#1a1e3a"/><text x="4" y="47" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="800" font-style="italic" fill="#1a1e3a">r</text><line x1="8" y1="125" x2="198" y2="125" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/><polygon points="8,125 16,121 16,129" fill="#1a1e3a"/><polygon points="198,125 190,121 190,129" fill="#1a1e3a"/><text x="4" y="117" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="800" font-style="italic" fill="#1a1e3a">s</text><line x1="148" y1="5" x2="80" y2="170" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/><text x="150" y="13" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="800" font-style="italic" fill="#1a1e3a">t</text><path d="M152,55 A27,27 0 1,0 113,82" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="138" y="43" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">115°</text><path d="M122,125 A27,27 0 1,0 83,152" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="106" y="158" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">x</text></svg>`}
function mkSvgComp(){return`<svg viewBox="0 0 180 165" width="165" height="150"><line x1="40" y1="140" x2="165" y2="140" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/><polygon points="165,140 157,136 157,144" fill="#1a1e3a"/><line x1="40" y1="140" x2="40" y2="18" stroke="#2563EB" stroke-width="1.8"/><polygon points="40,18 36,26 44,26" fill="#2563EB"/><rect x="40" y="124" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.4"/><line x1="40" y1="140" x2="90" y2="58" stroke="#1a1e3a" stroke-width="1.8"/><path d="M40,102 A38,38 0 0,1 61,109" fill="#BFDBFE" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="2" y="103" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#2563EB">34°</text><path d="M61,109 A38,38 0 0,1 78,140" fill="#D1FAE5" stroke="none" fill-opacity="0.8"/><text x="80" y="128" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">x°</text></svg>`}

const qs=[
  {q:"1. Triângulo retângulo (∠B=90°) com ∠A=37°. Qual é ∠C = x?",opts:["43°","53°","63°","127°"],c:1,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> 90° + 37° + x = 180° → <b>x = 53°</b>",svgFn:mkSvgTri1},
  {q:"2. Ângulos internos do triângulo: 2x (em A), 3x (em B), 4x (em C). Qual é x?",opts:["x = 15°","x = 18°","x = 20°","x = 25°"],c:2,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> 2x+3x+4x=180° → 9x=180° → <b>x=20°</b>",svgFn:mkSvgTri2},
  {q:"3. Ângulos suplementares: um mede 128°. Qual é o outro?",opts:["38°","42°","52°","62°"],c:2,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> 128° + x = 180° → <b>x = 52°</b>",svgFn:mkSvgSup},
  {q:"4. Retas paralelas r e s, transversal forma 115° em r. Qual é o ângulo correspondente x em s?",opts:["65°","75°","115°","180°"],c:2,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> Correspondentes = iguais → <b>x = 115°</b>",svgFn:mkSvgPar},
  {q:"5. Qual é a soma dos ângulos internos de um heptágono (7 lados)?",opts:["720°","840°","900°","1080°"],c:2,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> S=(7−2)×180°=5×180°=<b>900°</b>",svgFn:()=>`<svg viewBox="0 0 110 105" width="100" height="95"><polygon points="${polyPoints(7,55,52,46)}" fill="rgba(59,91,219,.1)" stroke="#3b5bdb" stroke-width="1.8"/><text x="55" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="13" fill="#3b5bdb" font-weight="800">900°</text><text x="55" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono,monospace" font-size="9" fill="#5a6490">7 lados</text></svg>`},
  {q:"6. Ângulos complementares: um mede 34°. Qual é o outro (x)?",opts:["46°","56°","66°","146°"],c:1,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> 34° + x = 90° → <b>x = 56°</b>",svgFn:mkSvgComp},
  {q:"7. Qual é a soma dos ângulos internos de um decágono (10 lados)?",opts:["1260°","1440°","1620°","1800°"],c:1,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> S=(10−2)×180°=8×180°=<b>1440°</b>",svgFn:()=>`<svg viewBox="0 0 110 105" width="100" height="95"><polygon points="${polyPoints(10,55,52,46)}" fill="rgba(12,166,120,.1)" stroke="#0ca678" stroke-width="1.8"/><text x="55" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" fill="#0ca678" font-weight="800">1440°</text><text x="55" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono,monospace" font-size="9" fill="#5a6490">10 lados</text></svg>`},
  {q:"8. Um polígono convexo tem soma dos ângulos internos de 1260°. Quantos lados possui?",opts:["7 lados","8 lados","9 lados","10 lados"],c:2,exp:"<b>Resolução:</b> (n−2)×180°=1260° → n−2=7 → <b>n=9 (nonágono)</b>",svgFn:()=>`<svg viewBox="0 0 110 105" width="100" height="95"><polygon points="${polyPoints(9,55,52,46)}" fill="rgba(232,144,10,.1)" stroke="#e8900a" stroke-width="1.8"/><text x="55" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito,sans-serif" font-size="12" fill="#e8900a" font-weight="800">1260°</text><text x="55" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono,monospace" font-size="9" fill="#5a6490">9 lados</text></svg>`},
];
let cor=0,don=0;
function buildQ(){
  const c=document.getElementById('qc');
  qs.forEach((q,i)=>{
    const d=document.createElement('div');d.className='q-card';d.id='qc'+i;
    const oH=q.opts.map((o,j)=>`<button class="opt" id="o${i}${j}" onclick="ans(${i},${j})">${o}</button>`).join('');
    d.innerHTML=`<div class="q-num">QUESTÃO ${i+1} DE ${qs.length}</div><div class="q-inner"><div class="q-opts-col"><div class="q-txt">${q.q}</div><div class="q-opts">${oH}</div></div><div style="flex-shrink:0">${q.svgFn()}</div></div><div class="q-exp" id="qe${i}">${q.exp}</div>`;
    c.appendChild(d);
  });
}
function ans(qi,ch){
  const q=qs[qi];
  document.querySelectorAll(`[id^="o${qi}"]`).forEach(b=>b.disabled=true);
  document.getElementById(`o${qi}${ch}`).classList.add(ch===q.c?'correct':'wrong');
  if(ch!==q.c)document.getElementById(`o${qi}${q.c}`).classList.add('correct');
  document.getElementById('qe'+qi).classList.add('open');
  if(ch===q.c)cor++;don++;
  document.getElementById('sq-c').textContent=cor;
  document.getElementById('sq-d').textContent=don;
  document.getElementById('sq-p').textContent=Math.round(cor/don*100)+'%';
}
buildQ();
</script>
</body>
</html>
